Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:45.92,Fate Apocrypha OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}迷いながら落ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:55.74,Fate Apocrypha OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}それぞれの思い選んだ道へ
